{"tid":111731,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"情人節大家送咩比男女朋友？","createTime":"2017-02-07T15:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T09:43:25.000Z","uid":11043,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c452789af3f1d76d5c83544bbd4d9004496d58b1","tid":111731,"uid":11043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:08:42.000Z","msg":"第一年過情人節 想送嘢比男朋友<br />\n完全無頭緒要送咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n銀包（佢果個好新淨）<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n散紙袋（整左個皮革嘅比佢）<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錶 （佢買左無耐）<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n帽 衫 褲 鞋 襪 袋（唔係送過就係佢有大把唔需要買住）<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n皮帶（佢好少用）<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n護膚品 （送過）<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDIY機關盒 （聖誕送咗）<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一餐飯 （平時都煮左）<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔想整朱古力/蛋糕咁行呀 大家有無收過啲咩難忘禮物/建議送咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 收到係會好驚喜好開心㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<del>同埋最唔想收到咩禮物都可以講下嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </del>"},{"pid":"96d92178ca4d76a56a9e2ab59c6c94eea03771e6","tid":111731,"uid":11043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:13:14.000Z","msg":"唉 2月情人節 4月頭一年 6月頭佢生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def652aec36ee7eafb70b37b7e4f4538ebd39bf3","tid":111731,"uid":8084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:15:59.000Z","msg":"有樣嘅杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有樣嘅綿花糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb944c1bb7bed67e6424f476d178fb600e499b03","tid":111731,"uid":10242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:16:48.000Z","msg":"無女朋友 想送都送唔到 <br />\nBlock哂我所有野"},{"pid":"ae969f1f3e1bf96bcd305f3c2011a89cb0e7add9","tid":111731,"uid":10242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:17:53.000Z","msg":"頭幾年都會自己諗送咩 <br />\n之後直情大家講想要咩<br />\n唔洗估估下"},{"pid":"10e1ef76277dead8d424e3ed9eaa450414527f70","tid":111731,"uid":46609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:40:43.000Z","msg":"你送咩佢都咁鐘意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有心意就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134c30e3eb86b3a076cb53f52f07434d71798f72","tid":111731,"uid":82747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:52:32.000Z","msg":"DIY啲手工勞作 幾有心思 雖然無乜實用性"},{"pid":"fbf37ab692dd948b8fc47a5f383017c6348954ef","tid":111731,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:55:07.000Z","msg":"寧願你俾佢口爆 送來送去麻鳩煩"},{"pid":"7038f2b2ec5e12986913d11fef785a87101c7e7c","tid":111731,"uid":61965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:55:51.000Z","msg":"送佢番屋企...如果我揾到嘅話"},{"pid":"1ee34a77a165279982104b2876eafe54bd7d8f43","tid":111731,"uid":8842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:56:09.000Z","msg":"整條美少女戰士鏈比佢"},{"pid":"00cad57a124d41186531d50b3f9305fba081f7f0","tid":111731,"uid":53966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:26:40.000Z","msg":"我整左個皮革袋俾男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4675174fd96467552d2a6014ce397b7600e315","tid":111731,"uid":11043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:28:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我整左個皮革袋俾男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm